	<h1 class="title">奥巴马为何咬定朝鲜黑了索尼？这要从 2010 年算起</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">David E. Sanger and Martin Fackler</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-21 09:49:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5424/medium/5424.jpg?1436687228" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="5424" data-title="《奥巴马为何咬定朝鲜黑了索尼？这要从 2010 年算起》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/5424/medium/5424.jpg?1436687228" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/5424" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
